149 Show dynamic products on frontend

Creating Models and Migrations for this module

> php artisan make:model Product -m
    change to migration file
> php artisan migrate

    Creamos el controller
> php artisan make:controller CartController 

    redireccionamos y creamos los archivos
Para hacerlo dinamico falta implementar las vistas...

150 Package Installation and setup

https://github.com/anayarojo/laravel-shopping-cart

> composer require anayarojo/shoppingcart

> php artisan vendor:publish --tag=config --ansi --force

    add debugbar
https://github.com/barryvdh/laravel-debugbar
> composer require barryvdh/laravel-debugbar --dev

    to the image File
.env File

FILESYSTEM_DISK=local

FILESYSTEM_DISK=public

> php artisan storage:link


